The CPSU canidates have won the elections, however a lot of our sponsored canidates have sucessfully gained seats in the All-Union Congress of Soviets, while nobody found out about our meddling. Stalin's Power has been put on a halt as he needed opposition support to continue his policy.

@let_the_ballot_cook
on-arrival:

Soviet Democracy once again took it's turn as the CPSU won elections once again. The Left opposition and anti-communists were defeated by the CPSU, while General Secretary Stalin is getting increasingly powerful due to the CPSU's popularity.
